The paper deals with generating background images from video sequences, which is a common problem in computer vision and image processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves image segmentation, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics). The use of algorithms and binary operations suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper's focus on generating background images using a simple assumption suggests that it may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
